summary: A better Ysolda using Skyrim NPC Editor by foretrenty
descriptionHtml:
This is my take on a better Ysolda inspired by my save file \'Lisa The Beautiful Nord\'!
You can find it here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=9253
Thanks to the user Raptor22HUN for giving me the idea for doing this.
Some people may not like it because it drastically changes the vanilla Ysolda but like I said before its inspired by my my other file Lisa.

*Recommended Mods*
Beauty Faces for females by necKros
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=1329

Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition 
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666

A big thanks to foretrenty for making the Skyrim NPC Editor
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=4554
